body: Hello .. now i played ranked for a whole season yet didnt get a loading screen border and i really got alot of honor and  i still level 3 honor so do i have a problem or something?

replies.body: It looks like you might not have qualified for some of the ranked rewards, but I would go ahead and hit up the EU support in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so they can take a closer look and make sure you weren't skipped.
It seems that you only played 2 games during the season, and the majority of your games are during preseason. You get your awards for what you earn during the season, not preseason.
got it now i know why ^_^ ty <3
